As the day winds down, interview sign-up sheets fill with names, and a whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews. Volunteers are stacking collapsed booths and gathering leftover brochures, contributing to the organization of the event. Healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos, highlighting their initiatives. Meanwhile, students compare swag items like water bottles and phone chargers.
